com.ibm.team.repository.common.query.ast

Interface IScalarFunction

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IFilterElement, ISelectionElement
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    INumericScalarFunction, IStringScalarFunction

    public interface IScalarFunction
extends IFilterElement, ISelectionElement
    Scalar functions operate against a single value, and return a single value based on the input value. Scalar Function can be a INumericScalarFunction or a IStringScalarFunction.
    Since:
    0.5
